": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340355, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": 2340344, "tag": null, "text": "这个对9.1号出生的人不太友好其实", "timestamp": 1629710993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": 2340355, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不是对9、10、11、12月出生者都不友好吗", "timestamp": 1629711053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "嗷，少打个之后", "timestamp": 1629711115, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340369, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是这个和教育公平有什么关系", "timestamp": 1629711168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340385, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": 2340369, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 因为有三分之一的人从出生就被剥夺了报考的权利呀", "timestamp": 1629711254, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340428, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": 2340385, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 创新班没有这个限制", "timestamp": 1629711817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340430, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": 2340385, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我们当时符合年龄条件的报少年班，不符合的报创新班", "timestamp": 1629711847, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 447944, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "科少里面全是变态", "timestamp": 1629712514, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 447944, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "不知道各位有没有了解过中科大的少年/少创班政策？dz当年曾经试图报名过（少创），但高一的时候被告知需要高二学籍才能报，高二的时候被告知年龄不符合（dz是十二月生人，比要求日期老了十几天，但入学年龄分界点是9.1，所以dz也无法早一年入学）大家觉得这样限制某些月份出生者不得报考的政策是否违反了教育公平的原则呢？", "timestamp": 1629710470, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629712511, "url": "", "vote": {}}}